videos.headline: Kentucky honors late O-line coach
videos.description: Wildcats leave a space empty on the offensive line and take a delay of game penalty in honor of coach John Schlarman, who died after a battle with cancer. Vanderbilt declined the penalty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky leaves spot vacant, takes penalty to honor late O-line coach) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky QB tears down the sideline for 32-yard TD
videos.description: Terry Wilson runs it 32 yards to the house to increase Kentucky's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky QB tears down the sideline for 32-yard TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Small scuffle breaks out between Vanderbilt-Kentucky
videos.description: Vanderbilt offensive lineman Grant Miller appears to throw a punch at a Kentucky player, but no flag is thrown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Small scuffle breaks out between Vanderbilt-Kentucky) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seals launches 34-yard pass to Pierce for a Vanderbilt TD
videos.description: Ken Seals connects with Chris Pierce Jr. in the end zone to get Vanderbilt on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Seals launches 34-yard pass to Pierce for a Vanderbilt TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson tosses 21-yard TD strike to Upshaw
videos.description: Terry Wilson finds Keaton Upshaw wide open for an untouched Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson tosses 21-yard TD strike to Upshaw) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rodriguez punches it in for Kentucky TD
videos.description: Chris Rodriguez Jr. powers his way into the end zone from three yards out to give Kentucky a commanding lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rodriguez punches it in for Kentucky TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rodriguez breaks through the hole for 74-yard TD
videos.description: Chris Rodriguez Jr. runs it 74 yards to the house for his second Kentucky touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rodriguez breaks through the hole for 74-yard TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET
